1. Introduction to SAP FICO
SAP FICO is one of the most in-demand modules in the SAP ecosystem. It powers financial operations in almost every large organization you can think of. The cool part? You don't need to be a hardcore coder or tech geek to learn it. If you understand business or have an interest in finance, this is your door to a high-growth career.
