2. Why SAP FICO Is Important Today
Ever noticed how companies always need smooth financial systems — even in a recession? SAP FICO experts help organizations manage:
•	Accounts
•	Budgets
•	Profitability
•	Audits
•	Financial reporting
Basically, if businesses are cars, SAP FICO is the engine that keeps everything running efficiently.
________________________________________
3. What Exactly Is SAP FICO?
SAP FICO = SAP FI (Financial Accounting) + SAP CO (Controlling)
Think of it like two halves of the same coin.
Financial Accounting (FI)
Handles things like:
•	Balance sheets
•	Ledger management
•	Bank transactions
•	Vendor & customer accounting
Controlling (CO)
Focuses on:
•	Cost management
•	Budget planning
•	Profit analysis
Together, they help companies make smart financial decisions.
